Package: talis-agent
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: System monitoring agent for Linux machines
 Talis Agent is a monitoring tool that continuously collects
 system metrics (CPU, memory, disk, I/O, and network usage)
 and sends them to a central API server. It also provides
 HTTP endpoints for receiving payloads and executing commands
 with proper authentication.
 .
 Features:
  * System metrics collection every 5 seconds
  * Regular check-ins with API server
  * HTTP server for payload management
  * Prometheus metrics integration
  * Secure token-based authentication 